posting_body: ['Reveal at Rye 220', '220 Bammel Westfield Road, Houston, TX, 77090', 'Use this link for more information:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 45', 'OR Text', '45', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text us.', 'THE REVEAL AT RYE 220 APARTMENTS IN HOUSTON', 'This is a Studio, 1 Bath, approximately 297 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Find your new home at the crossroads of comfort and convenience with The Reveal at Rye 220!', 'Our Houston apartments feature everything you look for in a place to call home.', 'With close access to restaurants, shops, parks, and entertainment, you can step into the local lifestyle right outside your door.', 'Here, the perfect combination of nature and city life is yours.', 'Visit local parks or grab a bite with friends at Cavo Coffee, Taquerias Arandas, or The Greasy Spoon.', 'Experience the best Houston has to offer and fall in love with our friendly community.', 'Come home to The Reveal at Rye 220 and come home to better living.', 'Contact us today!', 'Features', '- Fully Equipped Kitchen', '- Open & Efficient Apartments', 'Community Amenities', '- Professional & Responsive Management', '- Convenient Location', '- Newly Renovated Apartment Community', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 8:30AM-5:30PM', 'Saturday: 10:00AM-2:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Up to 2 pets per apartment.', 'Breed restrictions do apply.', 'Non refundable pet deposit.', 'See your community office for more details.', '$250.00 deposit and $25.00 pet rent.', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'g8cnWsyK']
